{
  "texts": [
    "The findings presented the extent of work done in 1 3 the area of TM from the perspective of bibliometrics.",
    "Our analysis showed there are more conference papers than articles overall, however, since 2019 there has been a significant proportion of articles published over conference papers.",
    "The results showed the most productive subject areas in terms of publications are computer science, engineering, social science, and mathematics.",
    "Our findings on the top countries, institutions, and citations revealed that China and the USA, are the two top countries in this field.",
    "Moreover, results showed that prolific authors of TM studies are from computer science subject area with minimum of 21 as h-index and have published at least 33 TM research papers."
  ]
}